comments: ["Absolutely loving the game so far! I'm relieved it's not another match 3 or merge 2 games, and really is about taking care of old dogs and managing the sanctuary. I've seen the game's advert for a long time, I regret not playing it sooner. But better now than never I guess! Only thing is the game keeps crashing on me occasionally while loading a new scene (ex; getting a new dog, loading livestream, .etc) I love the game and I want to support the funding, I'd appreciate a smoother experience. :')", "I played the game a while ago and recently reinstalled it, but now it won't even let me past level one. Everytime I try to stream it just makes the screen go black, and nothing happens. I've tried everything to fix it, reinstalling again, restarting my phone, even went online to try and find an answer. Love the game, just wish I could get further with it.", "I absolutely love this game! It's adorable, and I haven't experienced any bugs (I have played for about a month now). Though, for the Dog Blog, there are limited color options, which, as someone with bright green hair, is a little saddening :( Aside from my dramatics about hair color, I recommend everyone give this game a try! It's so customized, and each dog has their own favorite treats and toys, which is so fun to memorize. I love this game!!", "This game is really amazing and I love the style so much! I really like the game because it's supporting a real life senior dog sanctuary too! But last 3 or 4 days I couldn't get in the game because i got a message about some kind of error and I tried everything to get rid of it but it hasn't been working so far. I got pretty good progress there so it's going to be sad if i lose it. I don't know if its a game error or its like that for someone too but I hope it gets fixed soon!", "Very Cute very relaxing it's really wholesome too! But, I've been having issues lately When I stream the screen becomes black and the music keeps playing and I can't go to the next level because my first time of streaming is glitching I've been having Issues with that so whatever you could do please Fix it....", "First things first, this is not a game you will play for an hour straight. More like a few minutes at a time. Gameplay is fun though. Little thing I mentioned pre-edit, So basically my progress reset, (It has been fixed now.) Devs should probably look into what caused that. Also I don't know if the message I sent to tell them it was fixed worked? All in all, great game, great devs. (What caused the game to reset though?)", "A awesome friendly game where you get to experience adventures and journey with these adorable dogs and the amazing artwork! I love this game. It's just heartwarming. And there is so much more potential to expand apon! The fact that it was based on real dogs and experiences is also amazing. You get to read snippets of real-world inspiration the further you progress.", "This is THE BEST chill/idle kind of game I've ever played. There's so much to do! You are always getting rewards constantly, even past the early game. There are only ads very rarely, when you want to increase your rewards. The dogs are so sweet and have personality that you uncover through their individual story lines. You'll fall in love. I had this game ages ago and left it like I always do with mobile games (I'm fickle lol) and this is the ONLY game I missed so much I had to come back again!", "This game is fun but I got stuck on the streaming stage Everytime I tried the screen would go black to the point I just left and rejoin the game and when I kept trying it took my stuff but never worked if u could see if it's a bug please update Soo it doesn't happen to other people", "it was almost an amazing game, except for the fact that it was lacking in furniture and decoration aspects. it's fun caring for the dogs, but i wish i could put more furnitures. there's so many furniture blueprints, but i cant craft becuz the materials for good furnitures are so hard to get. i wish we could buy materials from donations, or we could get from streams. idk. im quite unsatisfied witht the reward rn", "This make me cry so much. I love idle games. I love that this is based off an actual doggy sanctuary with the actual doggies and with pictures of the actual doggies attached. I'm sad and happy and my heart melt. Some lags and bugs are experienced and the game crashes too. But i just love the concept of this game. Good strategy to make ppl adopt senior dogs and cry cause they're gone too soon", "It's really great especially for dog lovers! I Love it a lot and especially that it's also a real sanctuary.. It really makes me wanna donate now :( but my parents do not allow me sadly... I hope some people will still donate :) definitely will recommend some friends to play this..!", "Old friends dog adventure is such a fun game where you care for older dogs and play the challenges! You get to choose what to say and there's even a dog blog! Definitely would recommend.", 'Sancuaty names could be more customizable(wanted to name mine after my old pup, Timber.) But otherwise, The game is amazing. The graphics are great. The dogs are adorable. And I love the hat for Mack.', 'Absolutely what I was looking for in a game, perfect with little to no ads and with very reasonable microtransactions! Would recommend', "Very cute! I would love if the game would emphasize the importance of identifying dog-friendly costumes that won't bother dogs vs coatumes that will make them uncomfortable all day, but overall its super fun üëç", 'This Is such a heartwarming game, I love how simple are the interactions with the dogs. I love the little stories that they include of the dogs adapting to their new home. Amazing game!', "THIS GAME IS THE ACTUAL BEST! BAGEL IS SO CUTE MACK IS SO CUTE AND LEO IS SO CUTE,there's so many things to do!Decorate your sanctuary,collect new dogs,and it's all so much fun I love the theme and design of the game and how they're based on real life senior dogs!I wish I could meet them in real life!I was quite sad when I found out they only sold the merchandise in USD cuz I'm from the UK but seriously if I could I'd give this game a million bigillion stars out of a million biggilion stars!‚òÜ", "I am only on 3rd level, and I think it is really fun, cute, and great for a dog lover. I do find it a bit repetitive, but that will probably change over time. I olso do think Runaway's other games are really good too. If you delete their games, your progress will not be saved, though.", 'This game is so cute and entertaining! The dogs are adorable. Even the situations where almost nothing is going on it is really fun. Just baking food or cleaning the house just makes you feel happy and calm. I love this game and I really recommend this game for all dog lovers! ‚ù§Ô∏è', "It's such a cute game about dogs and don't love a dog for its age love it forever no matter what because old dogs are cute too and in the game you can unlock cute dogs like mack and bagel and Leo there so adorable doesn't matter how old a dog is love lasts for eternity I love Leo Babs and Captain Ron too runaway pls update maybe fix the bugs? Not asking for much ty the bug is it takes a bit to load and sometimes when I try saving a picture it says contact support game kicks me out any way to fix", 'I feel good playing with old friends, . I recently had to start a new game over because old friends got accidentally erased , I was devastated. Old friends helps me cope with losing my old friend scrappy. He was my everything, he passed away not long ago he was 16 and so loved. Thank you old friends for reaching out and I was very excited to hear from you. Thank you old friends.', 'This game is just so adorable, and the fact that it is based on real life dogs just makes it 10 times more interesting and unique! Love it, keep up the great work. ( I also totally recommend!)', 'This game is adorable and I love the concept of it. It is so cute and so fun, and i love that the dogs each have the personalities of the real pups. And favorite treats and toys. Babs is my favorite pupbso far hehe Ten stars from me!', 'Ohh, they have fixed the problem, the game is really wonderful, and very innovative, please I recommend you download it and give it a try', "So far, it's a really fun game! However I wish furniture was cheaper and there were more coupon codes. But overall, it's really good!", 'I love this game but my account got restarted and when i just wanted to play i was in the start again i dont know to get my stuff and my progress back please help i dont wanna start again.I still have the furniture that is needed coupons. But the ones i crafted is gone and the progress of the dogs are gone and i only have mack again', 'Edit: After 2 years of playing this game, it has become quite dull. The events are all repeats from the years prior... I already have all the rewards from the bake-offs, so why even participate? I have been at the max level for probably a year now. Not much to do after completing the stories. I have 3 senior rescues myself (2 dogs and 1 cat), so this game is perfect for me. I recently applied to vet school and want to focus on old animals. This game is everything I want out of life!!!', 'One of the first times a mobile game has truly felt like a game. Love oozes from every millimeter of this experience. Even the ads are non-intrusive, and from what I understand completely optional. Highly recommend!', 'Game has reset on me twice, erasing all my progress. The first time I used recover to get back to my original game. The second time it reset, I tried to recover my original game, but only the two previous reset games appear, making me start with zero progress. If this is not fixed, I will never play this again.', "Super cute and makes me feel better about playing mind-numbing games that get me nowhere. The only complaint I have is that the app randomly restarts sometimes after an ad video. Also, videos have been unavailable for me all day so I can't get Mack his chicken flavoring ü•π", "Love the premise behind the game and was enjoying playing it. The dog message requests bugged out with no images and did nothing when I clicked on them so I rebooted the game and it lost all my data :( I'm scared it will happen again.", 'This game is so much fun, and although you have to work very hard, the dogs are soo cute. Most relaxing game ever!', "It is amazing there's lots of adventures the dogs are so cute but the best thing is getting more of the dog's stories.", "This is a cute game and I enjoy it but I can't progress past the streaming part as the screen just goes black.", 'So far this is super cute and fun. a little bit slow, but really heartwarming and relaxing.', "Cute little game. I haven't closed it since download because I'm mildly afraid of missing things when my attention differs, but that's the only issue and isn't even really one! The whole app is so fun and adorable that I can't keep my hands off of it üôà", "I don't know why it's taken me so many years to download a wholesome game about dogs. So far into the game, it's easy to follow, lovely story and beautiful graphics. If you love dogs and want causal gameplay, this should suit you:)", "Love this game; it's so nice and wholesome! There has been issues with my progress resetting, but whenever that happens I breeze through the intro sequence then contact support through the game's settings, and they fix it in like a day. One thing I really wish the game had though is the ability to replay cutscenes, because the stories are just really cute.", 'Amazing game 10/10 never run iut of things to do, great asthetics, you just get to chill with good puppers, no annoying ads without consent and great atmosphere, highly recommend']

title: DogWorld - my cute puppy
description: The sweetest animal playing app DogWorld for everyone who always dreamt of having a dog. The cute little puppies are waiting for you to play with them. These dogs are true companions: you can take them anywhere and everywhere with you. Features üêæ The animal playing app for big and small dog lovers üêæ Your low-maintenance, virtual pet to play with and take care of üêæ Cool 3D graphics üêæ Collect stars to save for surprises üêæ Frequent updates and cool upgrades Your virtual dog for playing, petting and cuddling Your puppies react to touches on the touchscreen - this is how you can spoil them all around. They're always happy when you visit them because they're cuddly and playful dogs, who simply put everyone in a good mood. The more you play with them the more surprises wait for you: in every new level you'll receive a gift box with many accessories for your dogs plus treats and toys that every puppy loves. This puppy loves dancing and dressing up In this animal playing game you can do more than just pet and wash your pets. You have your own room where you can dress them up and photograph them. Your puppies loves posing for the camera. There are always new upgrades for the costume box so that it's never boring. In an additional room your dogs show you their lumbering dance moves to diverse songs that you can select. Good moods are guaranteed in DogWorld! For more information, visit us on Facebook facebook.com/tivolamobile
summary: Your own cute puppies to play with, pet and love

title: Dog Training App ‚Äî GoDog
description:
POSITIVE-BASED DOG TRAINING. BUILT-IN DOG CLICKER. TRAIN YOUR DOG ANYTIME, ANYWHERE!

Are you a happy dog owner? Do you want to know how to train your dog in easy-to-follow steps? Download GoDog ‚Äî smart guide for dog training and taking good care of your pet.

Here you will find a full lesson‚Äôs pack with step-by-step video instructions verified by professional dog trainers, built-in dog whistle and clicker, health and care diary, time walking schedule, useful articles, and other features that help your dog stay healthy and happy!

DOG TRAINER APP
These are easy-to-grasp and reproduce lessons for your dog that assist you with essential behavioral training. Teach your puppy to be socialized and well-adjusted without overpaying for dog trainer‚Äôs services. All lessons are made together with highly qualified dog trainers. 

You will find different lesson packages, such as Basic (sit, down, stay, no, paw), Good Pup Behavior (come, stop barking, chewing, don‚Äôt jump), Puppy Training Course (potty, collar, come on leash), Dog Tricks and Games, etc. We offer basic lessons for free.

HEALTH DIARY FOR KEEPING YOUR FURRY FRIEND FIT
With the GoDog Health & Care Diary, you'll never forget to take care of your pet. Create reminders for vaccinations, medications, visits to the vet, and other important events in your dog's life and save a history of these events. Track the hygiene care of your doggy including bathing, teeth brushing, nail clipping, ear cleaning, etc. Define dog schedule and let the GoDog app remind you when the next action is due.

WHISTLE AND CLICKER FOR TRAINING DOGS
Use these features to improve and strengthen the results of your dog training exercises. Dog clicker training is gaining popularity for its ease of use and positive effect. Download GoDog and use our built-in dog clicker with 3 different sounds!

WALKING TRACKER
Keep an eye on how much exercise your dog gets on a daily basis. It will help you adjust your walking routine to your dog‚Äôs specific needs.

DOG HEALTH ARTICLES
It‚Äôs extremely important to read up-to-date and verified information so as not to harm the dog. All information and articles in GoDog are checked by professional canine experts and vets, so you can have a rest, while learning something new about your fluffy friend.

Download the GoDog app now and start dog training and spending quality time with your four-legged friend!

Please feel free to contact us: info@godog.me
Privacy Policy: https://www.godog.me/privacy-policy

I love that you can teach your dog tricks and the app shows you how to gain trust with a dog, but overall this app is very great I recommend.', "Wow it's really working! My dog just learned how to sit in just a single minute! ü§©", 'Easy to use & understand. Contains the information I need', 'Amazing app,the guides help me to train my Rottweiler mix and it gives me an idea of what I should and should not do when training my dog.', "Honestly, amazing app, but a bit expensive for a phone app. Especially when it's subscription based. It's a training app, so technically once the dog learns the tricks, there's not added value from the app (no one pays to read articles that are free online) so a one time payment would've been reasonable, but I'm not payons 55 dollars a year to track walks! Too bad cause I would've loved to use it.", "The app works fine and does as intended, but to learn any of the good tricks you have to pay monthly or yearly. My dogs know all but one of the tricks that are unlocked. I got this so they could learn some more complicated tricks like roll over or sit pretty, not sit, stay, or paw. This app showed one good thing. One of my dogs learned paw. Please make it so I can learn the hard ones without paying. title: Dog Simulator - Animal Life
description:
If you do not have a real puppy in the house but you do want to get a pet to take care of it, if you like games with animals even if they are virtual ones then our application ‚ÄúPuppy Simulator‚Äù is a great option for your leisure time. Download our app for free on your smartphone or tablet and live an exciting life in a dog game.

Characteristics of the application ‚ÄúPuppy Simulator‚Äù 

You can make friends with an online good dog just downloading our program on your phone or tablet for free. Live and play like real dogs, acquire a family for your pet and learn something new about your favorite breed of dogs every day in this simulator.

Our adventure 3D game allows you to choose a domestic animal of a desired breed, to play with friends and their cute pets online in real time thanks to the multiplayer mode. Make friends in our puppy games, create real clans together to protect your family. The higher level your pet and its family is, the more breeds will be opened for you.

Advantages of the Dog Simulator application

There are such advantages in this dog game that you can appreciate:

1. The ability to create a pup as well as the whole family. Choose a nickname, a gender, a desired color, clothes and accessories in this animal simulator. Grow the beast and care for it. Find a mate and puppies for your pet so that your cub could have a great puppy playtime. Gain rewards, earn coins to unlock new breeds. Craft food on a fire.

2. The events take place in an exciting dogs games world where you can complete various tasks and set off on adventures. Live a dog life in a wild surrounding, look for animals such as squirrel, cat, rat and others to fight with. In pet dog games you won‚Äôt be boring because you will find enjoyment in leveling up your puppy, in discovering new combat achievements. Don't forget about communicating with dogs of other breeds as well as fighting against enemies in online animal games.

3. Our Simulation games supports 3D expansion. Discover unusual places and locations, nature and big cities, feel all the weather conditions and seasons. We did everything to make you feel yourself in a real world of doggy games.

4. The ability to play with friends online in online simulators. Bored of playing alone? Then turn on a multiplayer mode when you have an Internet connection, invite your friends in dog games. Together you can complete various tasks, fight against beasts enemies and protect your families.

All your personal and collective results will be accurately calculated and put into the leaderboard. Keep count of your points and take the first place in the leaderboard.

Try to download our application for free right now and feel all the advantages that animal simulators online can offer you in 2020!
summary: Do you like animal games? Install our dog games & puppy games if you like dogs!

title: Panda Games: Pet Dog Life
description:
Welcome to the Pet Dog Home! Are you ready to begin a cozy house life with your dogs? Adopt dogs, take care of them and play with them!

ADOPT DIFFERENT DOGS
14 adorable dogs of different breeds and colors are waiting for you to adopt. Each dog has its own personality! Adopt your favorite dogs and live in the pet dog home with them! There are surprises in every corner of the cabin!

TAKE CARE OF PET DOGS
The dogs' day starts with a delicious breakfast! Add dog food, and feed them well! After playtime, give your dog a nice bubble bath! Don't forget to monitor their health and treat the sick ones!

DRESS UP CUTE DOGS
Now, open your closet and dress your dog in cute clothes! First, let's wear a cape for your dog and then pick a nice bib for it. Last, put on a cozy little hat for your dog! Done! Your dog looks even cutter now!

PLAY WITH DOGS
There are so many toys that you can play with your dogs: frisbee, swing, and more! Play with your dogs in any way you like at the pet dog home! This will bring you closer together. Try different fun mini-games and exercise your brain while playing!

Download Panda Games: Pet Dog Life and spend some fun time with your dogs in the pet house!

FEATURES:
- 14 cute dogs available for adoption;
- Feed, bathe, dress up and take care of your dogs;
- Explore the Pet Dog House: living room, bedroom and playhouse;
- Plenty of dog toys: tennis, swing and frisbee;
- Many fun mini-games to play with your dogs;
- Supports offline modeÔºÅ

About BabyBus
‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî
At BabyBus, we dedicate ourselves to sparking kids' creativity, imagination and curiosity,and designing our products through the kids' perspective to help them explore the world on their own.

Now BabyBus offers a wide variety of products, videos and other educational content for over 400 million fans from ages 0-8 around the world! We have released over 200 children's educational apps, over 2500 episodes of nursery rhymes and animations of various themes spanning the Health, Language, Society, Science, Art and other fields.

‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî
Contact us: ser@babybus.com
Visit us: http://www.babybus.com

title: My Smart Dog: Virtual Puppy
description:
There are some smart puppies. Do you want to adopt them? They are waiting for you. In this game, you can own your beautiful house with a big garden and live with your puppies. In your big garden, you can walk and play with them. Maybe you can find something super cool! Smart puppies like to hide things to give you a nice surprise. Do you wanna it? Come on and let fun begin!

Help:
ü¶¥  Interact and play with your puppies.
ü¶¥  Feed puppies and enjoy your happy time.
ü¶¥  Go outsides to play with your puppies.
ü¶¥  If puppies are tired, let them have a good rest.

Features:
üçó  Unique painting styles and wonderful pictures
üçó  Rich backgrounds and massive props
üçó  Different mini games and ways of interactions
üçó  Exclusive adorable cute puppies 

They can‚Äôt wait to meet you. Don‚Äôt miss it! Download and play with them!

title: Duddu - My Virtual Pet Dog
description:
Let us introduce you Duddu, our new dog! He is a super nice dog who lives in a wonderful world full of fun and adventure. Become a part of Duddu‚Äôs everyday life and build a true friendship with your new virtual pet.

‚Ä¢ As a new pet owner, you are responsible for feeding, putting asleep, entertaining and looking after your own dog in his lovely house. In addition, you will have to take care of your scout dog in the wild as well!

‚Ä¢ Oops, Duddu needs doctor's help! Welcome to the animal hospital full of doctor games to give your dog the treatments he needs. Appoint him to the right vet‚Äôs office to solve a problem with fleas, stomach, leg, virus or wound. You can also pick some medicinal herbs and cook potions at the outdoor fireplace.

‚Ä¢ It‚Äôs time for a spa adventure! Have fun in the pool or sauna with Duddu‚Äôs pet friends and enjoy preparing smoothies or coloring mandala in the cutest pet beauty salon. 

‚Ä¢ Visit every corner of Duddu‚Äôs world and all of his friends, too. Take him on vacation to the sunny island with a cosy hammock and coconut palms. Customize your own pirate ship and teach Duddu different tricks at the dog school. Enjoy dancing in the club, exercising in the gym, painting and doodling in the gallery or playing drums and piano in the music centre. Have fun exploring the colorful world where the Sun goes up and down whenever you want.

‚Ä¢ Play over 30 different mini games and earn some coins or other goods. Have fun playing Bubble Shooter, Solitaire, Archer, Pirate Battle, Brick Breaker, Block Puzzle, Treasure Island, Moto Racer, Fruit Connect, Space Explorer, Hen Farm, various cooking games and many others. Go shopping and buy some unique pieces of furniture, food and clothes or customize your pirate ship and your house.

‚Ä¢ Complete daily challenges to learn about the dog‚Äôs habits and become a master of achievements to get some extra rewards. Check your mailbox everyday, you may find a surprise gift from a special friend.

This game is a guaranteed fun for people of all ages. Taking care of a pet gives you a sense of responsibility and loyalty. All you need to begin the fun journey is your own Duddu dog!

This game is free to play but certain in-game items and features, also some of those mentioned in game description, may require payment via in-app purchases which cost real money. Please check your device settings for more detailed options regarding in-app purchases.
The game contains advertising for Bubadu‚Äôs products or some third parties which will redirect users to our or third-party site or app.

This game is certified compliant with the Children‚Äôs Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) by FTC approved COPPA safe harbor PRIVO. If you would like to know more about the measures we have in place for protecting child privacy please see our policies here: https://bubadu.com/privacy-policy.shtml .

Terms of service: https://bubadu.com/tos.shtml

So I'm uninstalling this game.", 'Too many useless ads after you complete each level and also, the ads pop up after you touch a button.. That is just too annoying. Also, it doesn't allow you to use a stylus. Kind of odd. Garbage.", "Honestly I thought this game was gonna be very fun to play but when I opened the game there were like millions of ads that were 30 seconds long! I really think this game needs to be fixed! And plus when you try to turn off the internet you can't play the game! Also there are ads every second! THIS GAME NEEDS FIXING! NO ONE CAN ENJOY PLAYING THE GAME WITH ONE MILLION ADS!", 'I installed the game. Really njoyed playing it. But within few hours i uninstalled this game because of too much ads. Ads are coming continuesly after every level which makes the game very very irritating. For Playing every level need to watch adds. This is disgusting.', "I was about to installing this game after watching it‚Äôs gameplay on facebook. But when I noticed the reviews it disappointed me. It has too many ads like some other games. In short, we can say It's an ad which gives us a small time to play. I'm not installing it neither should you.", 'Like other reviews said, this game has way too many ads. Ads after each level and retry. Most of those ads are 30 seconds long, like seriously!? I spent 30 minutes and only reach level 10.', "I love the concept, i hate the ads. Uninstalled. Ads every 2 levels, or every 2 attempt, in case you're not successful from the start. Too much ad.", "App is good but after has infinite number of long Ad's. I played same game in iOS device and the app has no AD's. Not sure what happens with Android device, got pissed off with AD's and hence un-installing the application.", '5 stars are clearly bots , do not install this game , you can not turn off Ur WiFi to play it , they did that so you must watch all ads , too many ads , more precisely 30s unskipable add . I'm about to enjoy the game, but the ads just ruined my mood because there's ads almost every level and you cant skip it until it's done.", 'Win or lose there is a not so short ad at the start of every single level. If you want to accept a prize that the game offers you there is an ad. This game has more ad time than game time. It is unrelenting.', 'Fun game but the ads are pretty annoying, appearing after you end a level and in between. The app even slows down in the middle of the game.', 'Too many ads to be enjoyable. Easy levels so you finish the level in just a few seconds and have to watch a 30 second unskipable ad almost every time.', "This game can't survive without a data network. Its so annoying. Are the developers so snoopy that they want to collect every data of our activities. Uninstalling this derpy dog.", "It is a good game but, I draw one dot and it doesn't let me finish it. Other then that there are ads at every level. But still it's super fun.", "It's great and all but every time I fail the levels it just keeps playing an ad on my screen every single time which is really annoying.", "I thought about getting the game and when I read the reviews I cancelled the install. I'm sorry but if you won't let me play offline apart from the fact you need to school me grammarly ads Im Not gonna use your app.", 'Too many ads . Uninstalling this app because of the ads . Before every next level there is a 30 sec ad . If we lose 3 times , then there is a ad. Seriously ! Is this a gaming app or a ad app ?', 'Good game üëç. Just as we see in ads. But the game has A lot of ads. But atleast you can close the ads after 5 sec. Cross button top left corner.', "This game is super fun, when you're able to play it. The problem is that it's 75% ads. 10 seconds of fun play, now here's 1:30 of ads.", "Ads after every level and after every fail. 50% of the gameplay time is just ads, especially they are all 3 staged ads. Don't play this game unless if you are willing to watch 50 ads every 10 minutes.", 'More ads, more ads, more ads, more ads, it needs more ads! Not enough ads are in this game. It is unacceptable that there are few seconds I have to play and not watch more ads. I can watch ads only 99% of the time, but this long 1% of gameplay time is just too much for my taste!', "Game have some good tasks, but it's interface and smoothness is terrible, we can't draw line precisely even we have a bigger screen mobile. And also have ads.", "Ads are way too often and shoved down your throat. It feels like im trying to escape a maze when I'm trying to get out of some of these ads. 100% ruined the game for me because of this.", 'Game is funny. But ads very disturbing. If each level complete an ad come. If we play this game for time pass for 10 minutes around 6 minutes is wasted by unskippable ads', 'It took me soo long to download it but very good and fun game it allows you to draw anything like mommy long legs it so cool and even you cant save the dog by drawing anything you like and thats all thank you for reading._.:)', 'Ads are good for companies. However, this game contain too much ads. Every click an ad will appear even starting in level 1. Uninstalling the game.', "There are many many ads BUT they are not disruptive. the game is v playable, its addictive! I'm at level 85 and going higher aiming for 3 stars everytime!", "Ads are important to generate revenue, but they've so many ads that I played 55 levels in 35 mins and uninstalled the game because on every next click a new ad video shows up.", 'I used to like this game very much but now it requires wifi and also they added stars which take away everything I liked about the game because what I liked before was about being creative with the drawings.', "This game is very fine I must say but the stages are all the same like I can't get too difficult to challenge I but it is fun I would definitely recommended to other people like it's so fun", 'Paid for ads removal, but I wasted my money because there are still ads. Contacted both the game developer and google, both useless!', 'I use the ads as an excuse to get something else done, like answer text, msils, take a sip of my drink or eat lol. Patience is the key with these ads.', 'The worst game i have ever played, unlimited adds plus waste of time, I think they made this game for advertisement only, zero stars and should be deleted from play store,', 'I paid the ad free version, still sees annoying, inappropriate, uskippable ads. The game lags frequently. How can I get refund?', 'This game is good for playing. But there is a lot of ads, it will disturbing us very much, so, I rated it 0-1‚≠ê(Stars).']

title: Dog Cafe Tycoon
description:
Our new Tycoon game! The main character of this title is our eternal friend... Dogs!

Dog staff: Dog staff manage a variety of drink ingredients! They're kind, smart, lovely, and sometimes... playful!
üêï Milk-loving friendly Labrador Retrievers - Bailey
üê∂ Smart German Shepherd - Max
üê∂ Playful Beagle - Willy
üê∂ Brave Rottweiler - Diesel (You don't have to worry about stealing from the cafeüòâ)
Get more than 30 unique dog employees!
(Tell us your favorite dog and name it! We are interested in your opinion.)

Making drinks (Cafe operation): aromatic cafe lattes, sweet caramel macchiatoes, colorful unicorn frappe!
Serve quality drinks to dog guests who visit your cafe!
The drink on the first day of the cafe is simple. It's just coffee.‚òï
But the next day, I make caramel frappe latte!
Will the dog customers like the drink? The daily sales of the cafe tell the satisfaction of the dog customers!
Simulation to produce a variety of drinks day by day!

‚ùì‚ùì How do you manage a cafe with dogs? ‚ùì‚ùì
üÉè Collect various Dog manager cards.
üçπ Make a variety of signature drinks daily.
üí∞ Sell your drinks to customers!
üêï Competent managers help you.
‚òï You can decorate the cafe with gold earned by selling drinks.

It is the most üê∂friendly dogüê∂ cafe in the world.
You can enjoy this cafe offline.
summary: It's the friendliest Dogs game you've ever met!

comments: ["The ads don't bother me, the thing that I'm struggling with is it's way too hard to get the station's automated. Especially when you upgrade them you have then have enough cards to upgrade the dogs so that it can stay automated. Seems like I'm being punished for upgrading. Need to work on that balance, but I love the art and the ideas. But way bad balance issues. Feels like they want you to pay to play.", 'It\'s fun, but it needs some improvement. Most "error" messages are still in an asian language, not translated, so I do not know what they mean. The difficulty curve also suddenly becomes very high so you\'re just sitting there waiting a very long time to continue to the next level from level 6 or so on. Everything before that was a good pace. Also, way too many ads. Feels like it\'s ads for doing ANYTHING.', "It's cute, not glitchy, not laggy, however.. There is an air balloon that floats by and offers money in exchange for a video. That thing gets in my way so often it's aggravating. Not to mention it's really difficult to get sections to be automated because you don't ever get the chance to get more managers or the money to upgrade them. So in my opinion it's a well made game with a faulty system. It quickly becomes boring when you can't afford anything.", "The style and design is adorable and the ads don't bother me too much, it's what happens after the ads. The game freezes and stays that way for about 10 seconds and some times it stays that way and I have to exit the game and get back in. I rely on the rewards from ads but since the game doesn't work afterwards I'll skip the ads and the game", 'The game would be fine without a few things. Its monetization is absolutely horrid and does the #1 thing to piss me off. When turning in "quests" you can choose a bonus for watching an ad, or not; however, should you not you\'ll still occasionally get saddled with an ad that will take at least 5-10 seconds away. Then youll also get hit with another each time you "prestige". The actual economy itself is also built around either watching ads or microtransactions to progress. I cant fit the rest in.', "Wanted to like it due to art style, but ads are far too common and intrusive. First you force me to watch one for 15 secs, but I close that only for it to then load and play ANOTHER playable ad. Close that, nope I'm forced into ANOTHER damn ad screen. All for just 1 single damn box or to advance to the next day. Ads completely ruin it for me, so unfortunately it's just not that playable for me. If it was even tweaked a little bit, it could be decent.", 'This game has a cute concept, executed... not well. The UI feels very cluttered, with 5 different "limited offer" icons on screen that you can spend $5-10 to get in game items as well as an event icon, and a float-by "watch an ad" bubble that can\'t be dismissed that cruises by every minute. You get about three minutes of gameplay before hitting an ad, most of which are short but not all. Would be super cute, but awkward pacing and blatant money-hawking spoiled it for me.', "Absolutely adorable, however I HIGHLY suggest you play I airplane mode, or have a good add blocker, the game forces you to either watch adds regularly, or spend $30 USD on VIP pass which supposedly gets rid of the adds, I'd be willing to spend money on a game, but not that much. if adds don't bother you then maybe a random hot air balloon every few minutes blocking your ability to proceed briefly will? if none of that bothers you then I think you will like this game", "The game play is standard for a tycoon game but what makes it frustrating is early on, you run out of biscuits fast that are needed to upgrade your dogs. This makes it frustrating as you have quests requiring you use them but no consistent way of gaining them. Other tycoon games are a lot better about this and it's enough where I'm at a spot of just wanting to delete the game and play another.", "Since day 1 the bonus box that you can get by watching an ad hasn't worked! It just says no ads and I have unlimited data! No excuse for it not working and so frustrating when some of the missions request that you watch an ad and it doesn't work. Uninstalling it right now. More headache than it's worth.", "I would give this 5 stars because I love this game. I love it so much I have probably spent way too much money in it. But I have 1 big issue, and that's being stuck on day 24 for over 4 months. I finally got 1 quest done in hopes it'd boost me a bit more and I only got 3 more quests done. The quests are ridiculously hard for this Day to the point where I have to wait multiple days to even level a section up. And even then, it's not enough. It's ok to make days harder as they go but not this hard", "Don't let it's aesthetic fool you. This is a game that is so desperate for you to spend money it's willing to make the gameplay worse at every point until you do. I really wanted to like it but it's actually so much more viciously designed to frustrate than most other similar games that I decided after only a few levels it simply wasn't worth it.", "I really like this game so far. However, I think it's a bit excessive to wait so long for the free gift box and the rotating purchasable cards. I also stopped encountering the Welsh Cookie Jar ads which makes many of the tasks impossible for me to complete in order to progress through to the next stage.", "The game is fun up until a certain point. After the first few levels I realized that there is constantly soo many things moving or blocking something I want to tap. The art style is cute but once you get over that it's gets boring quickly.", "As many other reviews have said. Other tycoon games with automatic manager cards do it much better. It's slow to make progress and is luck based whether you get manager cards to advance which only comes in a gift box that take hours to renew. You also need biscuits to upgrade which rarely appear. You'll spend more time watching ads for coins that barely impact anything and get stuck waiting for the gift box for a card than actually playing the game.", 'Game has too many ads, most are "optional" but it makes them in the way of gameplay and pretty necessary to progress at a reasonable pace. $25 to get rid of them is too high a cost. Don\'t install.', "I've spent more time watching non-mutable ads than actually playing the game. Also every 10 seconds a floating balloon takes up 1/3 of the playable screen and asks you to watch an ad for money. This game would be so cute and fun if it was playable", 'Fun until watching so many ads to get ahead gets to a point where you no longer can progress in the game fast enough. Stuck at day 8 with no way of getting more upgrades to move things along. Tired of watching ads and doing the same thing all hour...', 'The game has too many ads. If you play 15 minutes of the game 50% of it will be taken by ads. It\'s really not got alot of content. Sometimes you can voluntarily not watch the ads, but sometimes they sneek in the button that forces you to watch a "short ad". I hate how much advertising there is ok the game to make you spend money, along side the millions of ads you have to watch. It is not child friendly due to the amount of ads. The 5 star ratings feel fake and were bought.', "Just an app to watch ads. I don'tind ads in games but i spend more time watching ads in game then playing the game. Even when given the option to skip the ad and get less of a bonus it STILL plays the add. It's super annoying", 'Tutorial has no ads. After the tutorial the gameplay is literally unplayable because of ads popping up everywhere, floating across the screen and forcing you to watch to progress at all. I would give this game -1 star if I could', 'Im currently playing the game and it keeps sending me to the playstore to download an app, there was no ads everytime it did that, its making it difficult to play cause i have to exit the playstore and reenter the game. Fix this bug.', 'I really wanted to like this game but the amount of ads and the ad balloon flying over the tasks so you click on it instead of the task is too much. Gave it a try, do not recommend!', "It's a fine game. But you need to make sure to watch ads get bonus mission reward. If not, you need to throw in cash. Not very free2play game. The bone cookies are too less for each ads reward.", 'Too many adds! Could hardly play the game for adverts that kept on being shoved in front of the screen. Then they swap the buttons so you accidentally click the button to not get adverts only to end up with more adverts. Too many adverts for such a pretty game', 'The game is really cute and relaxing. But overall the "error" is really getting on my nerves & theres too many ads like its everywhere. But its still fun for me and cute, I recommend this game for relaxing and if your into cute games ‚ò∫Ô∏èüêæ', "Cute game but the art style of the ads and actual game do not match. Not what I came for. There's also no customization unlike what the game description insinuates, it's a conveyor belt assembly game. Ads will also autoplay even if you decline the giftbox so what's the point of letting me say no?,", "Balloon gets in the way when I'm trying to tap dogs that I can't automate yet, either have the balloon be an icon on the side like the biscuit jar or let me toggle the balloon on and off. I'd rather have random pop up ads than a balloon that gets in the way. Also let me sell extra manager cards for bones so I can afford to automate", "Day 2 for me and it's been good so far, keep in mind that this game is like those types that resets after you clear the day. It can be a painful to see all the stuff you collect (game time) gone after you accomplish one day", "The ads are a bit too much. I usually don't mind them, but there's a lot Also that stupid reward balloon constantly get sin the way and makes me miss things", 'Cute but way too many ads. It has ad based objectives and every time you start a new level the music turns back on.', "I like this game but the problem is why can't we just buy new servings? I thought it was gonna be like that other cooking cat game, but it is way different!", 'You need to watch a "short" ad at random times to complete the tasks you patiently waited for?
